column5: here are a few of the fish i've caught and released since july1 this year               so...am i a fisherman or what !!!!
Way to go Paul! Welcome to the dark side.
Nice variety of fish there & that sunfish was hungary Richard
Great report. Looks like you've had a great summer so far! Thanks for sharing.
Good stuff Paul.  I come for the link ups, but I stay for the pics!!  Nothing wrong with releasing your catch either.  Don't like the taste?!
